# <type>(<scope>): <subject>  — 50 chars max, imperative mood, no trailing dot
#
# <body>  — wrap at 72 chars; explain *what* and *why*, not *how*.
#
# <footer>  — breaking changes, issue refs, Co-authored-by, etc.
#
# Types:  feat fix docs style refactor perf test build ci chore revert
# Scope:  optional, one word, lowercase (e.g. parser, ci, deps)
#
# Examples:
#   feat(parser): support trailing commas in arglists
#   fix(ci): pin actions/checkout to v4 to avoid node16 deprecation
#   refactor!: drop Python 3.8 support
#
# Lines starting with '#' are ignored.
